            <h3>Building meaningful, purposeful relationships</h3>
            <p class="hilitd">We're here to help your diners feel good, and most imporantly, do good just by trying out <strong id="sidebar_restaurant_name"></strong></p>
            <h5>Here's how it works again:</h5>
            <p><strong>You</strong> share you're a "Buy One, Feed One" establishment and pick a dish to donate.</p>
            <p><strong>Diners</strong> give $1 or greater for your dish online</p>
            <p><strong>We</strong> get 100% of purchases to charity, and report monthly on groups you met</p>
            <p class="hilitd">
                We'll send you debut materials to use once you sign up. Expect a <strong>4x-6x</strong> immediate return on your investment to becoming a <em>"Buy One, Feed One"</em> establisment.
            </p>
            <p>We start all restaurants out at $50/mo, which grows as your traffic grows. Cancel anytime.</p>
