            <form id="signup">

                <h1>Tell Us About Yourself</h1>
                <p>Always feel free to give us a call too (616-61-FOOD-6) if you have questions or prefer to sign up that way. Our email is hey@foodcircles.org. If you're into snow, feel free to engage with us in person. Or visit the team page and get in touch directly. Come to an event like the Happy Hour Carol Tour and sing songs.</p>  

                <input type="text" name="name" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Your Name">
                <input type="text" name="email" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Your Email">
                <input type="text" name="restaurant_name" class="field standart input" placeholder="Your Restaurant's Name">
                <input type="text" name="restaurant_address" class="field standart input" placeholder="Your Restaurant's Address">
                <input type="text" name="restaurant_neighborhood" class="field standart shifted-input" placeholder="Your Restaurant's Neighborhood (if applicable)">
                <input type="text" name="website" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Website">
                <input type="text" name="facebook" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Facebook Link">
                <input type="text" name="twitter" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Twitter Link">
                <input type="text" name="instagram" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Instagram Link">
                <input type="text" name="social_contact" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Social Media Contact">
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="social_contact_same"> Same as Above</label>

                <input type="text" name="pricing" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Pricing ($-$$$$)">
                <input type="text" name="phone" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Phone Number">
                <input type="text" name="first_dish" class="field standart input" placeholder="First Dish to Promote (typically appetizer or dessert">
                <input type="text" name="first_dish_price" class="field standart shifted-input" placeholder="Price on menu">
                <label>
                    <input type="file" name="">
                    Photo of Your First Dish (Optional)
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="file" name="">
                    Photo of Exterior or Interior (Optional)
                </label>

                <h1>Set Up Payment</h1>

                <input type="text" name="cc" class="field standart input" placeholder="Credit or Debit Card Number">

                <input type="text" name="exp" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="Expiry">
                <input type="text" name="cvc" class="field standart small-input" placeholder="CV Code">

                <p class="small">
                    * Your card will not be charged until you are live on site and app. Always feel free to give us a call too (616-61-FOOD-6) if you have questions or prefer to sign up that way.
